---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";

import client from "../../data/client.json";
import Landing from "../../components/Landing.astro";

// Optimize our landing image and pass it as props to the BaseLayout (for preloading) and Landing (for rendering)
import {getOptimizedImage} from "../../js/utils"
import landingImage from "../../assets/images/cabinets2.jpg" // <-- THE PATH TO THE ASSET YOU WANT TO PRELOAD - The asset must live in src
const optimizedImage = await getOptimizedImage(landingImage)
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Solo & Family"
  description="Meta description for the page"
  preloadedImage = {optimizedImage}
>
  <!-- ============================================ -->
  <!--                    LANDING                   -->
  <!-- ============================================ -->

  <Landing 
    title="Solo & Family"
    image={optimizedImage}
  />

  <!-- ============================================ -->
<!--             Side By Side Reverse             -->
<!-- ============================================ -->

<section id="sbs-r-870">
  <div class="cs-container">
    <!-- Image Wrapper for Stacking -->
    <div class="cs-images-wrapper">
      <!-- First Image -->
      <picture class="cs-picture">
        <!--Mobile Image-->
        <source media="(max-width: 600px)" srcset="/assets/images/familyplay-1-mobile.jpg">
        <!--Tablet and above Image-->
        <source media="(min-width: 601px)" srcset="/assets/images/familyplay-1.jpg">
        <img
          loading="lazy"
          decoding="async"
          src="/assets/images/familyplay-1.jpg"
          alt="family play"
          width="630"
          height="775"
        >
      </picture>

      <!-- Second Image -->
      <picture class="cs-picture">
        <!--Mobile Image-->
        <source media="(max-width: 600px)" srcset="/assets/images/familyplay-2-mobile.jpg">
        <!--Tablet and above Image-->
        <source media="(min-width: 601px)" srcset="/assets/images/familyplay-2.jpg">
        <img
          loading="lazy"
          decoding="async"
          src="/assets/images/familyplay-2.jpg"
          alt="golf coaching"
          width="630"
          height="775"
        >
      </picture>

       <!-- Second Image -->
       <picture class="cs-picture">
        <!--Mobile Image-->
        <source media="(max-width: 600px)" srcset="/assets/images/familyplay-3-mobile.jpg">
        <!--Tablet and above Image-->
        <source media="(min-width: 601px)" srcset="/assets/images/familyplay-3.jpg">
        <img
          loading="lazy"
          decoding="async"
          src="/assets/images/familyplay-3.jpg"
          alt="golf coaching"
          width="630"
          height="775"
        >
      </picture>
    </div>


    <!-- Content Section -->
   <!-- Content Section -->
   <div class="cs-content">
    <span class="cs-topper">Featured Service</span>
    <h2 class="cs-title">Solo and Family Golf Play: A Fun and Rewarding Experience</h2>
    <p class="cs-text">
      Discover the joy of golf with our Solo and Family Golf Play packages, designed to bring people together and create unforgettable experiences on the course. Whether you're looking to enjoy a serene solo session or plan a fun outing with family, we offer tailored options for golfers of all ages and skill levels. Golf is more than just a game—it's an opportunity to connect, unwind, and create lasting memories with loved ones.
    </p>

    <h3>Why Choose Our Solo and Family Golf Play Packages?</h3>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Flexible Options for Every Skill Level:</strong> From beginners to seasoned players, our golf play packages cater to all abilities, ensuring a welcoming environment for everyone. Whether you're a novice learning the ropes or a pro refining your skills, our courses are equipped to meet your needs.</li>
      <li><strong>Family-Friendly Atmosphere:</strong> Bond with loved ones in a relaxed and supportive setting. Our family packages include activities and challenges that make the game enjoyable for all age groups, encouraging participation and fun.</li>
      <li><strong>Scenic and Well-Maintained Courses:</strong> Tee off on beautifully landscaped courses that cater to both solo and group play. Our carefully designed layouts and pristine greens offer an ideal setting for a perfect game.</li>
      <li><strong>Customized Solo Sessions:</strong> Focus on your game with quiet, uninterrupted solo play, ideal for practicing techniques or simply enjoying the calm of the course. Our solo sessions are designed for those who value their time on the greens.</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>What We Offer</h3>
    <h4>Solo Play Packages</h4>
    <p class="cs-text">
      For those seeking personal time on the course, our solo play sessions provide:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>Peaceful, distraction-free gameplay in a serene environment, ideal for relaxation and focus.</li>
      <li>Access to dedicated practice areas, including driving ranges and putting greens, for honing your skills.</li>
      <li>Opportunities to play at your own pace, ensuring a stress-free and enjoyable experience.</li>
    </ul>

    <h4>Family Play Experiences</h4>
    <p class="cs-text">
      Create lasting memories with your family through our fun-focused packages:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Family-Friendly Tee Times:</strong> Enjoy flexible tee times designed to suit families, complete with shorter course options for younger players.</li>
      <li><strong>Group Challenges:</strong> Engage in fun group challenges and team-based formats that keep everyone entertained and motivated.</li>
      <li><strong>Coaching Support:</strong> Our friendly coaches are on hand to assist families new to golf, ensuring every member feels confident and included in the game.</li>
      <li><strong>Junior Golf Programs:</strong> Special sessions and games tailored to younger golfers help foster a love for the sport while developing skills in a fun and supportive way.</li>
    </ul>

    <h4>Additional Perks</h4>
    <p class="cs-text">
      Our Solo and Family Golf Play packages come with extra benefits to enhance your experience:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>Affordable membership plans for frequent players, making golf accessible and budget-friendly.</li>
      <li>Seasonal discounts and special offers for family groups and larger events.</li>
      <li>Access to exclusive tournaments and family-oriented golf events throughout the year.</li>
      <li>Opportunities to connect with a community of like-minded golf enthusiasts in a friendly environment.</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Start Your Golfing Journey Today</h3>
    <p class="cs-text">
      Golf is more than just a game—it’s a way to connect, unwind, and create lasting memories. Our Solo and Family Golf Play options are designed to bring people together and provide an enriching experience for golfers of all ages and skill levels. Whether you’re refining your game during a peaceful solo session or sharing the joy of the sport with loved ones, our packages offer the perfect opportunity to enjoy the game in a way that suits you best.
    </p>

    <p class="cs-text">
      Every moment on the greens is a chance to bond, learn, and grow. From the quiet focus of solo play to the shared laughter of family outings, our thoughtfully crafted experiences ensure that your time on the course is as meaningful as it is enjoyable. Discover how golf can bring balance, relaxation, and connection to your life, one swing at a time.
    </p>
    <a href="/services/equipment" class="cs-button-solid">Equipment</a>
  </div>
</div>

  </div>
</section>


